The paper deals with a computer vision problem of image matting and proposes a deep learning-based algorithm to solve it. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning and convolutional networks, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also mentions the creation of a large-scale dataset, which could suggest that it belongs to cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.MM (Multimedia).
